The JoLT algorithm is described in:
    Krishnan, R. & Schulz, V. "A JoLT for the KV Cache: Near-Lossless
    KV Cache Compression via Joint Tucker and JL-Residual Allocation
    for LLMs." arXiv:2607.12550, 2026.
